ciples said, “first let me go bury my father.”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:8:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But Jesus told him, “Follow me, and let the dead bury their own dead.”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:8:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"As he got into the boat, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 4:36–41","book":"Mrk","chapter":4,"verse":36,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 8:22–25","book":"Luk","chapter":8,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 6:16–21","book":"Jhn","chapter":6,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" his disciples "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 10:1","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":1,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 26:56","book":"Mat","chapter":26,"verse":56,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 3:7","book":"Mrk","chapter":3,"verse":7,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 16:20","book":"Mrk","chapter":16,"verse":20,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 6:13","book":"Luk","chapter":6,"verse":13,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 12:16","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":16,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"text","text":" followed him. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 4:36–41","book":"Mrk","chapter":4,"verse":36},{"label":"Lk 8:22–25","book":"Luk","chapter":8,"verse":22},{"label":"Jn 6:16–21","book":"Jhn","chapter":6,"verse":16},{"label":"Mt 10:1","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":1},{"label":"Mt 26:56","book":"Mat","chapter":26,"verse":56},{"label":"Mk 3:7","book":"Mrk","chapter":3,"verse":7},{"label":"Mk 16:20","book":"Mrk","chapter":16,"verse":20},{"label":"Lk 6:13","book":"Luk","chapter":6,"verse":13},{"label":"Jn 12:16","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:8:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Suddenly, a violent storm arose on the sea, so that the boat was being swamped by the waves —but Jesus kept sleeping. "}],"crossRefs":[],"