"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" to the region of the Gadarenes, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read Gergesenes"},{"kind":"text","text":" two demon-possessed men met him as they came out of the tombs. They were so violent that no one could pass that way. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 5:1–17","book":"Mrk","chapter":5,"verse":1},{"label":"Lk 8:26–37","book":"Luk","chapter":8,"verse":26}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read Gergesenes"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:8:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Suddenly they shouted, “What do you have to do with us, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss add Jesus"},{"kind":"text","text":" Son of God? Have you come here to torment us before the time?” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jdg 11:12","book":"Jdg","chapter":11,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Sm 16:10","book":"2Sa","chapter":16,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 1:24","book":"Mrk","chapter":1,"verse":24,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 4:34","book":"Luk","chapter":4,"verse":34,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 2:4","book":"Jhn","chapter":2,"verse":4,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 8:7","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":7,"letter":"f"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jdg 11:12","book":"Jdg","chapter":11,"verse":12},{"label":"2Sm 16:10","book":"2Sa","chapter":16,"verse":10},{"label":"Mk 1:24","book":"Mrk","chapter":1,"verse":24},{"label":"Lk 4:34","book":"Luk","chapter":4,"verse":34},{"label":"Jn 2:4","book":"Jhn","chapter":2,"verse":4},{"label":"Ac 8:7","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Other mss add Jesus"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:8:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"A long way off from them, a large herd of pigs was feeding. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:8:31","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“If you drive us out,” the demons begged him, “send us into the herd of pigs.”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:8:32","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Go!” he told them. So when they had come out, they entered the pigs, and the whole herd rushed down the steep bank into the sea and perished in the water. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:8:33","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then the men who tended them fled. They went into the city and reported everything, especially what had happened to those who were demon-possessed. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:8:34","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"At that, the whole town went out to meet Jesus. When they saw him, they begged him to leave their region. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Kg 17:18","book":"1Ki","chapter":17,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 5:8","book":"Luk","chapter":5,"verse":8,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 16:39","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":39,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Kg 17:18","book":"1Ki","chapter":17,"verse":18},{"label":"Lk 5:8","book":"Luk","chapter":5,"verse":8},{"label":"Ac 16:39","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":39}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279616815}